data.description: Newer home in a great community!! Sage Homes built the home in 2020 and the sellers have added a few of their own touches. Some upgrades include, ceiling fans throughout, all new blinds, 2nd floor living area transformed into 4th bedroom, & some front yard landscaping. 4 bed - 3 bath & an unfinished basement ready for your finishing touches. The main floor provides lots of natural light and a fireplace to cozy up by. Outside you have a nice large back yard to be able to entertain the whole family! Don't miss this move in ready home, call your agent today! All information obtained from seller and public records.
